image_analysis.description: A photograph showing the interior of a closet or storage area. On the left, there is a white wire shelving unit with several drawers labeled with contents. On top of the shelving unit are stacked books and boxes. To the right of the shelving unit is a hanging rod with wooden hangers, one of which holds a bright blue hooded sweatshirt. The background consists of beige walls and a white shelf below the hanging rod. A watermark 'EFTA00000037' is visible in the bottom right corner.
image_analysis.layout: The image is divided into a storage shelving section on the left and a hanging clothes section on the right.
